=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Matthews, pp. xv\u2013xvi.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Matthewsxvi-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-Matthewsxvi_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Matthewsxvi_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-Matthewsxvi_5-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Matthews, p. xvi.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.maryjones.us/jce/barddas.html\">\"Jones\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">March 9,</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Jones&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.maryjones.us%2Fjce%2Fbarddas.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABarddas\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rolleston2010-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rolleston2010_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">T. W. Rolleston (30 January 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=1AKmnxWMnGQC&amp;pg=PA227\"><i>Myths and Legends of the Celtic Race</i></a>. Digireads.com Publishing. pp.&#160;227\u2013. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-4209-3507-3\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1-4209-3507-3\">978-1-4209-3507-3</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <spa